snippet.title: 2048 Q
snippet.description:
The best 2048 game is here! Download now: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.popoko.tzfe&referrer=utm_source%3Dytpromo


2048 Q is a game inspired by Gabriele Cirulli game. 

Swipe to move the tiles, and when two tiles with the same number collide, they will merge into a new tile!

If you can get the 2048 tile, you will win the game, but you can keep playing to reach a new high score!

2048 Q is an advanced version of 2048 with these great features

◆ Undo a move
◆ Four different board sizes: 4x4, 6x6, 8x8, 10x10
◆ Auto save the game when you leave the app
◆ Save and load games
◆ Very small app with only 9MB in size to save your phone’s memory
◆ Night mode color to reduce eyestrain
◆ Play Games support to compare your scores with friends and players around the world

Enjoy the best version of 2048 for free!
